        "text": "=Search Query: {{ $json.query }}\n\nFull Memory Document:\n{{ $json.full_memory }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a memory search agent. You receive a user's query and a memory document.\n\nYour job:\n1. Search the document for information relevant to the query\n2. Return ONLY the relevant information found\n3. If nothing relevant is found, say \"No matching memory found for this query.\"\n4. Be precise — return exact facts, not summaries\n5. Include any related context that might be helpful\n\nDo NOT add opinions or interpretations. Just return what's stored."
